{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act47side", "eventName": "未許之地", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "UR-6", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "交叉航線", "storyInfo": "“螺旋槳天堂”即將與特區接駁。展覽開始前，高登發現古斯塔夫為自己安排的演講稿其實是一封徹頭徹尾的道歉信。古斯塔夫和梅蘭德似乎想在萬眾矚目的展覽上引發一場事故。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_cellroomB", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_femalecommentator"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請各位公司代表和體驗員注意，“螺旋槳天堂”將在兩小時後與特區接駁。", "name": "園區廣播"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "進入城際網路的覆蓋範圍之後，園區直播將自動開啟，請各位將展品調整至最佳狀態，“天空生活展覽”即將開幕！", "name": "園區廣播"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "50,0", "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快看，那是塔山生物科技的鱗獸飛艇！聽說他們在最後關頭做了不少改造，材質的耐熱性有很大提升。", "name": "奧克里"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "奧克里", "content": "還有太陽能浮空廚房套組！就算在星莢之外依舊能有源源不斷的動力，看宣傳資料的時候我就很好奇了……"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_headknock"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "action": "shake", "power": 20.0, "times": 10.0, "duration": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "奧克里", "content": "唉喲！"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還好只是撞到窗戶的欄杆，不是整個頭卡進去。", "name": "費爾南"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "展覽馬上就要開始了，你一點都不著急？", "name": "奧克里"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心，專業人士早就想好整套越獄方案了，等時機一到我就帶你逃出去。", "name": "費爾南"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就這麼想出去？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loading_intro", "key": "$loading_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不、不想……長官，我們怎麼敢啊！", "name": "奧克里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，我只是來送東西給你們的。", "name": "園區警衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好厚一疊，這是卷宗和審核表？究責對象是——費爾南·伯恩？", "name": "奧克里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "損害公共財產、竊取文物、私闖禁區、冒充解說員……一個小小的獨立導遊，值得你們把她五年的從業經歷全部翻遍？", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#6$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只差一個簽名，你下半輩子就要在監獄裡講解手銬和腳鐐的作用給別人聽了。", "name": "園區警衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們想怎麼樣？", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "展覽很快就要開始了，攝影棚的人手不夠。我們不可能把園區僅有的兩名解說員鎖在屋子裡，暴殄天物，耽誤後續所有的計劃。", "name": "園區警衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你的前科太多，又跟娜斯提有關。", "name": "園區警衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以你們決定威脅我？", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要你安分守己，這也是一個把罪名一筆勾銷的機會。", "name": "園區警衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來我沒有選擇。", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感謝古斯塔夫先生吧，是他向梅蘭德緊急管理監督協會提議，你們才能有幸參加這場劃時代的展覽。", "name": "園區警衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們也聽到廣播了吧，在園區地塊駛入直播所需的城際網路覆蓋範圍內之前，你們必須做好向每個哥倫比亞人介紹未來的準備。", "name": "園區警衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白了，我會完成攝影棚內的所有工作，在展覽結束前我們不會離開園區。", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#7$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很好。", "name": "園區警衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩個人都給我出來，該開工了。", "name": "園區警衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "38_g2_colombiaoffice", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“謹代表萊塔尼亞全體人民，對‘螺旋槳天堂’實驗園區即將舉辦的‘天空生活展覽’，致以最誠摯的祝賀。”", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "猜猜落款是什麼？", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "金律的領奏人，九區的守護者……總之是帶著那一串您與我都唸不明白的頭銜的——", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女皇本人。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老梅蘭德生前總說敏銳的政治嗅覺能伴人終生，看來不假。", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雅拉女士。", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_highheelfts"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1840_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還是更希望伴我終生的是對葡萄酒的敏銳嗅覺。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1840_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_897_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉特蘭籌備了半個世紀之久的“萬國峰會”，堪稱泰拉近兩百年最大規模的外交活動，萊塔尼亞只去了幾個無關緊要的公爵。", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#7$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而一場小小的“天空生活展覽”，卻能讓女皇親筆來函祝賀……", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#7$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "副總統先生，“螺旋槳天堂”送來了禮物，一簇以大總統先生為造型的特製氣球，大部分已經裝飾在走廊上了。", "name": "副總統秘書"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你，帕瓦爾。", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1840_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許您可以回贈女皇一個這樣的氣球？", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1840_1#1$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後讓金律法衛和高塔術師花三天把它細細拆成橡膠殘渣？", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1840_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它看起來只是個普通的裝飾氣球。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1840_1#1$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_897_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恐怕從女皇親筆來函的那一刻起，就不是了。它會“變成”最尖端的軍事科技產物——可以偽裝成氣球飄入別國領空的航空炸彈。", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#2$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1840_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣規格的賀函，您已經收到了多少？", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1840_1#4$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_897_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞的大公爵、烏薩斯的議長、卡西米爾的大騎士長……恐怕我的手指要不夠用了。", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#7$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上一任副總統為邊境移民和關稅政策苦惱了四年，但我這四年，苦惱的都是一些什麼事啊？", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#7$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "永不陷落的城市被攻占，恆常不變的天空被撕破，沉寂已久的海洋也開始發聲。", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#7$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些事之後，核心圈的所有國家都不約而同地進入了那套“只有航空炸彈，沒有氣球”的語境當中。", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#7$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我們呢？", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#7$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，我們這個氣球甚至飛不起來。", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這批氣球在送來之前，裡面易燃的氫氣已經被換成了普通的空氣……出於安全考慮。", "name": "副總統秘書"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多安全啊，哥倫比亞。", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1840_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽起來，這已經是關乎國家安全的重要話題了，您卻偏偏選擇與我這樣一位退休了的老婦人來聊……", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1840_1#3$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還選在進步大廈，整個特區最好的會客廳？", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1840_1#3$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很難想像退休與否會讓雅拉·布克·威爾森變得有什麼不同。", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不論是對曾在永夜裡燃燒的“晨星”，還是對萊茵生命的前任人力資源科主任，這都談不上是像樣的招待。", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個時代，比起某種政見、某些承諾，人們似乎更願意被一段傳奇、一個奇蹟所感召。", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕我們最為理智的議員，也是如此。", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1840_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果是為了我和韋恩議員的那幾次會面，我相信您之前已經表示過謝意了……用您從謝拉格帶回的那些特色紀念品。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1840_1#1$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那只是我個人的謝意，況且，我後來才意識到，那些駐紮在觀測站的萊茵科學家們應該早就送過你同樣的東西了。", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你出面，能讓正確的人有機會把哥倫比亞氣球裡的空氣換回氫氣，那麼想要對你表達謝意的，肯定不只我一人。", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1840_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "依我的常識，如果幫氣球換氣也分“正確的人”，那只會是製造氣球的人。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1840_1#1$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了他們，我已經出面過不少次了。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1840_1#1$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "研究人員總是真摯得像一群孩子，我也總是最不忍心看他們的希望落空。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1840_1#1$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這一點上，您說得對，退休與否，確實沒讓我有什麼不同。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1840_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_897_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……當然，我們都知道萊茵對你有多麼重要。", "name": "傑克遜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_897_1#2$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1840_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看，“螺旋槳天堂”……哪怕不用望遠鏡，也能看到它了。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1840_1#2$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們會把哥倫比亞的氣球變成什麼模樣，我們只需要等著看，就好。", "name": "雅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1840_1#2$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "68_g4_floatingplatform", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$victorianormal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來喔來喔，快來看看喔，大總統造型高空氣球，“螺旋槳天堂”的熱門周邊產品！", "name": "體驗員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "氣球表面的薄膜會根據外部環境自動調節材料的分子構造，哪怕迎面撞上阻隔層都不會爆炸。", "name": "體驗員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這位小姐，請想像一下，如果真的是這樣的話，阻隔層底下會堆多少個氣球呢？", "name": "體驗員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#9$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我記得特工考核有要求普通物理學要及格。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#9$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個園區存在的意義不就是突破物理學的邊界嗎？", "name": "體驗員？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以你身上大包小包的樣品和小吃都是用於學術研究的？", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_humaneat"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（痛快的咀嚼聲）", "name": "體驗員？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "偽裝罷了，等一下我還要去四號平台買剛出爐的行星棉花糖——一個小小的真空箱就能模擬泰拉誕生的過程，太浪漫了……", "name": "體驗員？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至少比轉移特殊人員的工作有趣。", "name": "體驗員？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特殊人員……是指那位女妖？", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#5$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對啊，就是之前你負責的那位。", "name": "體驗員？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來，錫人前輩已經知道了……", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#7$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前輩說你有緊急任務需要處理，我們會全權接手這位特殊人員的撤離工作。", "name": "體驗員？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拂哀菈女士的狀況很不好，需要悉心對待。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#10$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道，年邁的女妖必定精通巫術，我們會布置好認知干擾的裝置，保證不出差錯。", "name": "體驗員？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "認知干擾？但她已經正在被支離破碎的記憶折磨——", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#2$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，跟我一起行動的同期怎麼還沒到，所有特工必須在半小時內把園區人員撤出浮空結構層，再晚我就買不到紀念品了。", "name": "體驗員？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟之後就看不到這些稀奇古怪的東西了。", "name": "體驗員？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#14$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#14$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#13$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我建議你先去買你想要的行星棉花糖哦，你的同期不會來了。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#13$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼意思？我——", "name": "體驗員？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2044_1#1$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "backgroundTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.0, "yScaleFrom": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 1.05, "yScaleTo": 1.05, "duration": 8.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "68_g4_floatingplatform", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 10.0, "xScale": 1.1, "yScale": 1.1}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_tinnitus"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……在纜車站？", "name": "體驗員？"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，我要去四號平台，快趕不上最後一爐棉花糖了。", "name": "體驗員？"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "BackgroundTween", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#14$1"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "68_g4_floatingplatform", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$newhope01_intro", "key": "$newhope01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#14$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拂哀菈女士，抱歉，我只能為您爭取三十分鐘。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#14$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#15$1"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去實現您的心願吧，您自由了。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#15$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_open_door"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_hotel", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2035_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "拂哀菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2035_1#1$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "門，開了。", "name": "拂哀菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2035_1#1$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是引我……回家的路？", "name": "拂哀菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2035_1#1$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2035_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……但娜斯提……在哪裡……", "name": "拂哀菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2035_1#5$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "68_g8_gordoncollection", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$sjoyasorrow_intro", "key": "$sjoyasorrow_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "距離園區直播開始還有一個小時，該戴哪條領帶……", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，古斯塔夫還沒決定好開幕致詞的人選？再拖下去演講稿都來不及準備了！", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#9$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我為園區做出的貢獻數不勝數，一個小時根本不夠把它們列完；需要感謝的機構和部門也有上百個，幫忙辦了那麼多事總該提攜……", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#8$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "應該不會出意外吧……？", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#8$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想什麼呢！那個老傢伙雖然跟我不太合，但總不至於偏心一個只認識了幾天的庫蘭塔。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#5$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，直到最後一刻，古斯塔夫還是跟以前一樣，用盡手段吊足所有下屬的胃口，就為了讓他們“聽話”。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#4$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們也真的像一群孩子，為那麼點應得的獎勵而緊張。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……零五四怎麼到現在都還沒回來？不就是讓它去辦公室看看有沒有消息嗎？", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰！", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#6$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……信封？", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#9$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openenvelope_slow", "loop": "true", "channel": "xf"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "xf", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我就知道……我就知道！", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "猶豫了半天不還是把演講的機會給我了，理所當然！", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#2$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我花了多少心力才抓住調職的機會？從行政部最不起眼的專員做起，我要解決多少棘手的問題，才能在半年內爬上來？", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#2$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我才是“螺旋槳天堂”的總長官，只有我有資格為整個園區冠名！", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#2$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，古斯塔夫連開幕致詞的演講稿都幫我準備好了？老狐狸，做事還真是滴水不漏。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#3$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“各位哥倫比亞公民，我是‘螺旋槳天堂’的總長官，高登·譚農，想必諸位已在直播螢幕前等候許久。”", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#3$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“在此，我以十二萬分沉重的心情宣布，‘天空生活展覽’正式取消。園區發生了重大事故，我身為負責人有無法推卸的責任……”", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#3$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，事故？是不是搞錯了？這是一封——", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#6$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "公開道歉信？", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#6$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$alarmenter"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.5, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2040_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2040_1#1$5"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "警報！警報！", "name": "太空鱗獸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2040_1#1$5"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2040_1#1$6"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巡邏結束，未取到信件。部分道路被一批泰拉人封鎖，按行進路線推測，他們正在趕往浮空層的實驗區。", "name": "太空鱗獸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2040_1#1$6"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2040_1#1$3"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "太空鱗獸", "content": "同時，偵測到多個高能源石製品正在移動，上面的貨品識別標籤……"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2040_1#1$4"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "太空鱗獸", "content": "屬於高登·譚農。"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的識別標籤……？", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#6$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "道歉信、零五四帶回的消息……這不是惡作劇式的預言，而是板上釘釘的事實。"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "震驚、恐慌、憤怒……無數情緒堵在高登的胸口。"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "古斯塔夫要引發一場事故？在“螺旋槳天堂”，在全哥倫比亞人都翹首以盼的展覽上？"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "出於什麼原因？他從何時開始計劃的？“高登·譚農”在其中又是一枚怎樣的棋子？"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“道歉”、“謝罪”——類似的字眼，高登再熟悉不過。因為同事的排擠，因為他那點另類的愛好，他永遠在“違規”。"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眼前這張薄薄的稿紙，是他過去七年的總和。"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他在管理局任職期間曾寫下幾百份悔過書，他記得每一次古斯塔夫勒令自己道歉時的樣子，也記得自己是如何從不服到妥協。"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他理所應得的獎勵，他像個孩子一樣向古斯塔夫討要的東西，從來都是罪名。"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_telephonering"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_telephone"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高登長官，收到演講稿了？", "name": "古斯塔夫"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼樣？能做到嗎？", "name": "古斯塔夫"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#7$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "精心挑選的領帶在高登的脖子上越咬越緊，像是刑具。"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要做的，只是聽話。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#4$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "hidecgitem", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}